flowchart TB
    subgraph Clients["Enterprise Clients"]
        WEB[React Frontend]
        API_CLIENT[Internal APIs]
    end

    subgraph Gateway["Centralized Control Plane"]
        KC[Keycloak SSO]
        KONG[Kong API Gateway]
        OPA[OPA Policies]
        REDIS[Redis Quotas]
    end

    subgraph Orchestrator["FastAPI Orchestration Engine"]
        IC[ML Intent Classifier]
        ROUTE[Deterministic Routing Map]
        STREAM[SSE Streaming]
    end

    subgraph Providers["AI Providers"]
        OLLAMA[Ollama on-prem]
        EXT[External LLM APIs]
    end

    subgraph Data["Data & Observability"]
        PG[(PostgreSQL + RLS)]
        PROM[Prometheus / Grafana]
        VAULT[HashiCorp Vault]
    end

    WEB & API_CLIENT --> KONG
    KC -.->|JWT RS256| KONG
    KONG --> OPA & REDIS
    KONG --> Orchestrator
    IC --> ROUTE --> STREAM
    STREAM --> Providers
    Orchestrator --> PG & PROM
    VAULT -.->|secrets| Orchestrator
